    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Repair your outdoor gear with this Gear Aid 2pc Tenacious Tape and Adhesive Bundle Set!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">GEAR AID 2pc Tenacious Tape and Waterproofing Gear Repair Sealant Set (4 Styles)</h2>\n  <p>Repair your outdoor gear with this Gear Aid 2pc Tenacious Tape and Adhesive Bundle Set!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>ALL IN ONE REPAIR SOLUTION - Includes Tenacious Tape and your choice of waterproof adhesives - Aquaseal or Seam Grip - for comprehensive outdoor gear repair.</li>\n    <li>DURABLE, WATERPROOF TAPE - Peel-and-stick Tenacious Tape repairs holes and tears on nylon, vinyl, rubber, plastic, and more; it&#039;s washable and won’t peel over time.</li>\n    <li>INVISIBLE &amp; STRONG REPAIRS - Choose from clear or ripstop nylon tape for subtle, reliable fixes on jackets, tents, tarps, and other camping gear.</li>\n    <li>HEAVY-DUTY PUNCTURE FIXES - Flex Patches included for rugged repairs on inflatables, sleeping pads, and high-use outdoor equipment.</li>\n    <li>WATERPROOF ADHESIVES INCLUDED - Aquaseal and Seam Grip seal seams and protect against water damage, keeping your gear adventure-ready.</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72205/arMD1KY7IPGuusGeL3z6FqpJzdZZ4l-metadHRhcGVfc2VhbGFudF9wYXJlbnQuanBn-.jpg\" alt=\"Repair your outdoor gear with this Gear Aid 2pc Tenacious Tape and Adhesive Bundle Set\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <p>Use Tenacious Tape to fix holes and tears quickly on technical/synthetic fabrics, including vinyl, nylon, rubber, and plastic gear. It’s a peel-and-stick, weatherproof repair tape that’s washable and won’t peel over time. It sticks to jackets, tents, and tarps, staying put no matter what Mother Nature dishes out.</p>\n  <p>Instantly make a tent repair with Tenacious Tape in ripstop nylon or clear tape for a barely noticeable solution. Tenacious Tape also comes in a tough, flexible nylon fabric strip for jackets and other camping gear. For inflatables and sleeping pads requiring heavy-duty fixes, use puncture-resistant Tenacious Tape Flex Patches. When outdoor gear gets ripped or torn, Tenacious Tape will handle it, allowing you to stay outside longer.</p>\n  <p>We&#039;ve also included 2 adhesive options - Aquaseal and Seam Grip. The Aquseal and Seam Grip are both waterproof sealants designed to seal and protect your outdoor gear from water. Grab this set of adhesive and tape to ensure your gear is ready for your next outdoor adventure!</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
